Title: Rabbit learns he is adopted - YouTube
Descript: A free roam rabbit/free range rabbit sleeping. When the rabbit sleeps, the rabbit often dreams. Pipkin rabbit eats, runs, and jumps in his dream, and his sleeping body does the same. After the rabbit is told he is adopted, he wakes up, makes a ferocious yawn, and sneezes, and allows himself to be pet. Waking a sleeping rabbit by telling him he is adopted may not sound very nice. However, Pipkin is a tiny pet bunny rabbit who loves waking up humans. So, every once in awhile, we wake him up. The rabbit has been woken with a rabbit air horn and a rabbit firecracker. When the rabbit is sleeping he often dreams of eating something, or doing one of his rabbit eating ASMR videos. When the rabbit eats in his dream, he sleeps soundly, and it takes more effort to get the rabbit to wake up. Here the rabbit is fast asleep, until he learns he is adopted!Maybe you saw our waking a sleeping rabbit with an air horn video, or waking a sleeping rabbit with a firecracker video or waking a sleeping rabbit with a guitar video. This is the same idea, just WAY more intense.Again, don't worry that we woke up the sleeping rabbit with the shocking news. The rabbit takes about 20 naps a day, and the rabbit wakes up at the quietest opening of the refrigerator door. Pipkin is always ready to make a rabbit eating ASMR video - so even when he is asleep, he is vigilant for sounds someone might feed him, as the rabbit loves eating fresh fruits and vegetables!When the rabbit is sleeping and dreaming, you can hear the rabbit smacking his lips and licking his lips. Watching him and listening to the rabbit sleep can be very calming. The sounds the cute rabbit makes can be relaxing, too. The rabbit sleeps out in the open usually. However, later at night, or for an afternoon nap, he likes to cuddle on the couch. Oftentimes he falls into the REM sleep, where he dreams and moves about. He is a free range rabbit, or free roam rabbit, and he has free range of the house. Maybe that's why the rabbit always likes to sleep out in the open, in the middle of the room or under the futon. Ha! Silly rabbit!Thanks for checking out Pipkin and our rabbit channel. We hope you think this is the cutest rabbit video ever, because he really enjoyed making this video! If you'd like to see more cute rabbit videos, please watch some of our other work!Please click here to subscribe! https://goo.gl/bJFo8GOther stuff we’re doing!Instagram: one.more.pleasePipkin’s Amazon store: https://goo.gl/m1gdkBPlease let us know if you have any feedback or suggestions! Thank you!! :D#rabbits#cute#wakingasleepingrabbit

Title: The Chance to become a Mother - Dean Schneider - YouTube
Descript: I‘ve spent a lot of time thinking about this Moment for the past few Months and even though it felt wrong I always came to the conclusion to sterilize Nayla before she has her first litter! But when the Vet arrived I knew if we do it NOW there is no going back anymore! We are not into trading animals, we are closed to the public (no Tourism) and have lots of natural african property! The Hakuna Mipaka Pride has a life-long and wild home here at the HM Oasis and I am not taking in any further Lions anymore. So in the end of the Day, it’s only going to be Nayla, Kiara, Khaleesi, Dexter, Snow & Leo which are going to have 300 hectares (3Million sqm) of pure african nature to roam, play, hunt and life a beautiful life! Extending this pride with a few more family members will increase their success in hunting and give the pride more natural responsibilities and social interaction with one another.Besides this I couldn‘t look into Naylas Eyes anymore knowing that I decided to take her ability away to become a mother before she even had the chance to give it a try! In this Case i‘m just letting nature be nature as far as the Environment and space on the Hakuna Mipaka allows.The Chance to become a Mother - Dean SchneiderSubscribe:  http://bit.ly/subDeanSchneider | Follow my IG: https://www.instagram.com/dean.schneiderFollow Dean Schneider:Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/schneiderdean/ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dean.schneider Tiktok: https://tikitoks.com/@deanschneider.o... Official Website: https://www.deanschneider.com/ Support Hakuna Mipaka Oasis: https://www.deanschneider.com/donatio...About Dean Schneider: I am a 27-year old Swiss guy, who dedicated his entire life to the animal world! Nowadays, I live in Africa, I am a member of a lion pride, my wife is a hyena and I’m a daddy of two monkeys. Besides that, I have built a global voice for our planet’s wildlife over the past two years!Born in Switzerland (Zurich) on October 3, 1992, I was blessed to grow up in a loving family with my sister (one year older) and my parents, who were always very supportive and loving. My mother is originally from the Balkan region (Southeastern Europe), while my dad is a Swiss citizen. I discovered my deep passion for wildlife at the age of six or seven, through the legendary Steve Irwin! He was the one who brought wildlife into my living room in Zurich and inspired and educated me about all kinds of different animal species.Even though I was so passionate about animals, I originally followed a very ordinary path to adulthood, eventually ending up in the finance industry as a financial advisor. After a very successful year, I decided to found my own company, which then, over the next three years, allowed me to generate the financial foundation to launch the Hakuna Mipaka project at the age of 23-24.After starting my life in South Africa additional financial support form my Family allowed me to evolve and develop the Hakuna Mipaka Oasis for 2 Years without having to depend on any income sources such as offering touristic visits / programs, breeding or trading of animals, donations or any other monetary businesses! About Hakuna Mipaka:The Hakuna Mipaka Oasis is located on around 400 hectares (four million square meters) in the wilderness of South Africa! It is home to thousands of different wild animal species! Besides that, the oasis also serves as a life-long home to a few rescued wild animals, which were born in captivity! We also do rehabilitation programs with different animals, which are then being released back into the wild.The Hakuna Mipaka Oasis is my personal home and a private sanctuary that is NOT open to the public. We don’t cater to tourists and don’t allow any day visits or animal activities! We don’t breed animals and we are also not trading animals. I built this place for animals and not for humans. The Hakuna Mipaka oasis is a secure, wild & lifelong home to the animals that live here.#DeanSchneider #FORMAT #VIDEOSPECIFIC

Title: Customizing My Shoes - YouTube
Descript: Hey Guys! Today I am going to be painting and customizing a pair of shoes. They are some cheap knock offs of Vans, but still. They came out really cute. I really enjoyed this process, it was really fun, and there are so many possibilities, especially if you are willing to do something different on each shoe.This can also be a cool way to up cycle old shoes, or just a way to pass the time if you are currently bored at home. It's a really easy art project to cure your quarantine boredom. OR, just enjoy watching me do it, that too <U+0001F606> Wear Shelly and Eustace: https://moriah-elizabeth.teespring.co...SUPPLIES I USED (contains affiliate links):Angelus Leather Paint (big bottles): https://amzn.to/2QzjUmGAngelus Leather Paint (small bottles): https://amzn.to/2U5gmuoVinyl Red Tape: https://amzn.to/2WHjhLRHigh Gloss Acrylic Finisher: https://amzn.to/2J4mCwc___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh <U+0001F602> ) and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 25 and like doing anything creative...and being snarky.....just a lil. I make a lot of decorating and painting videos here. I'm obsessed with editing and adding lil bits to my videos, so if that's not your thing....oof you may hate this haha. I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and other random things I pick up. I also love to draw, but don't expect anything too skilled, I'm not the best at that haha. You will also find occasional crafting/testing crafting kits on my channel which are always a hot mess. And even some baking (REALLY bad at that, but it's fun to try LOL). Descript: AMAZING BREAKFAST IDEAS FOR A WEEKENDI’m sure that you have at least one egg in your fridge and it means that you can prepare super delicious and quick breakfast. Take an empty plastic bottle and combine yogurt, eggs, sugar and flour.  And now you can cook pancakes from the bottle. You can even make a cake. Watch the tutorial! We share a cool way to prepare coffee using an orange. Check out the incredible tutorial! One more crazy recipe is chicken cooked in watermelon. I bet you haven’t known how delicious it is! Title: TERUGKIJKEN: Rutte en De Jonge over coronamaatregelen - YouTube
Descript: Het kabinet kwam met een korte update na het crisisberaad over de coronamaatregelen. Grote veranderingen werden niet verwacht en bleven ook uit. \We hebben geen nieuwe besluiten genomen maar wel de situatie uitvoerig met elkaar besproken\", zegt premier Rutte. \"Het beeld op straat is gemengd. Op Koningsdag was het onwerkelijke plaatje te zien van een grotendeels leeg straatbeeld. Maar je ziet het ook drukker worden op straat. Meer mensen komen naar buiten, ook als het niet echt nodig is. Dat is niet zonder risico.\"\"In de zorg gaan de cijfers de goede kant op. Maar in de ziekenhuiscijfers zit een vertraging. Mensen kunnen het pas na een paar weken merken. En dan kan het ook nog zo zijn dat iemand die naar het ziekenhuis moet, pas een paar weken later naar de IC gaat. De ziekenhuiscijfers zijn een kostbaar bezit, maar ook een gevoelig bezit.\"\"De algemene adviezen blijven daarom gelden. Blijf zo veel mogelijk thuis. Werk zo veel mogelijk thuis. Bij klachten blijft het hele gezin thuis. Winkelen is geen uitje. Het openbaar vervoer is voor mensen die naar hun werk moeten, niet voor plezierreisjes.\"Meer video's? Title: The Chance to become a Mother - Dean Schneider - YouTube
Descript: I‘ve spent a lot of time thinking about this Moment for the past few Months and even though it felt wrong I always came to the conclusion to sterilize Nayla before she has her first litter! But when the Vet arrived I knew if we do it NOW there is no going back anymore! We are not into trading animals, we are closed to the public (no Tourism) and have lots of natural african property! The Hakuna Mipaka Pride has a life-long and wild home here at the HM Oasis and I am not taking in any further Lions anymore. So in the end of the Day, it’s only going to be Nayla, Kiara, Khaleesi, Dexter, Snow & Leo which are going to have 300 hectares (3Million sqm) of pure african nature to roam, play, hunt and life a beautiful life! Extending this pride with a few more family members will increase their success in hunting and give the pride more natural responsibilities and social interaction with one another.Besides this I couldn‘t look into Naylas Eyes anymore knowing that I decided to take her ability away to become a mother before she even had the chance to give it a try! In this Case i‘m just letting nature be nature as far as the Environment and space on the Hakuna Mipaka allows.The Chance to become a Mother - Dean SchneiderSubscribe:  http://bit.ly/subDeanSchneider | Follow my IG: https://www.instagram.com/dean.schneiderFollow Dean Schneider:Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/schneiderdean/ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dean.schneider Tiktok: https://tikitoks.com/@deanschneider.o... Official Website: https://www.deanschneider.com/ Support Hakuna Mipaka Oasis: https://www.deanschneider.com/donatio...About Dean Schneider: I am a 27-year old Swiss guy, who dedicated his entire life to the animal world! Nowadays, I live in Africa, I am a member of a lion pride, my wife is a hyena and I’m a daddy of two monkeys. Besides that, I have built a global voice for our planet’s wildlife over the past two years!Born in Switzerland (Zurich) on October 3, 1992, I was blessed to grow up in a loving family with my sister (one year older) and my parents, who were always very supportive and loving. My mother is originally from the Balkan region (Southeastern Europe), while my dad is a Swiss citizen. I discovered my deep passion for wildlife at the age of six or seven, through the legendary Steve Irwin! He was the one who brought wildlife into my living room in Zurich and inspired and educated me about all kinds of different animal species.Even though I was so passionate about animals, I originally followed a very ordinary path to adulthood, eventually ending up in the finance industry as a financial advisor. After a very successful year, I decided to found my own company, which then, over the next three years, allowed me to generate the financial foundation to launch the Hakuna Mipaka project at the age of 23-24.After starting my life in South Africa additional financial support form my Family allowed me to evolve and develop the Hakuna Mipaka Oasis for 2 Years without having to depend on any income sources such as offering touristic visits / programs, breeding or trading of animals, donations or any other monetary businesses! About Hakuna Mipaka:The Hakuna Mipaka Oasis is located on around 400 hectares (four million square meters) in the wilderness of South Africa! It is home to thousands of different wild animal species! Besides that, the oasis also serves as a life-long home to a few rescued wild animals, which were born in captivity! We also do rehabilitation programs with different animals, which are then being released back into the wild.The Hakuna Mipaka Oasis is my personal home and a private sanctuary that is NOT open to the public. We don’t cater to tourists and don’t allow any day visits or animal activities! We don’t breed animals and we are also not trading animals. I built this place for animals and not for humans. The Hakuna Mipaka oasis is a secure, wild & lifelong home to the animals that live here.#DeanSchneider #FORMAT #VIDEOSPECIFIC

Title: TERUGKIJKEN: Rutte en De Jonge over coronamaatregelen - YouTube
Descript: Het kabinet kwam met een korte update na het crisisberaad over de coronamaatregelen. Grote veranderingen werden niet verwacht en bleven ook uit. \We hebben geen nieuwe besluiten genomen maar wel de situatie uitvoerig met elkaar besproken\", zegt premier Rutte. \"Het beeld op straat is gemengd. Op Koningsdag was het onwerkelijke plaatje te zien van een grotendeels leeg straatbeeld. Maar je ziet het ook drukker worden op straat. Meer mensen komen naar buiten, ook als het niet echt nodig is. Dat is niet zonder risico.\"\"In de zorg gaan de cijfers de goede kant op. Maar in de ziekenhuiscijfers zit een vertraging. Mensen kunnen het pas na een paar weken merken. En dan kan het ook nog zo zijn dat iemand die naar het ziekenhuis moet, pas een paar weken later naar de IC gaat. De ziekenhuiscijfers zijn een kostbaar bezit, maar ook een gevoelig bezit.\"\"De algemene adviezen blijven daarom gelden. Blijf zo veel mogelijk thuis. Werk zo veel mogelijk thuis. Bij klachten blijft het hele gezin thuis. Winkelen is geen uitje. Het openbaar vervoer is voor mensen die naar hun werk moeten, niet voor plezierreisjes.\"Meer video's?
